Github tutorial 
1) how to create a repository?

* create a repo in github.com 
* make a file (README.md)
*

2) how to clone a repository

* in terminal 
  git clone (copy paste)repository link from Github

3) how to update a repository

* git add .
* git commit -m "updated"
* git push -u origin master

4)

* in repository page go to settings end of the page
* click 'delete repository'  button

